## This file contains the hardware specification for bingo the robot ##

Device list / role:

Arduino Mega - interface to sensors and actuators
ESP 8266 module - provides WiFi functionality to Arduino
Stepper motors x2 - Main actuators of robot, connected to wheels
Stepper motor driver boards x2 - control the stepper motors and connect to arduino
Ultrasonic sensor - to calculate distance to objects infront of robot, for obstacle avoidance
Ir sensor - to calculate distance to objects infront, for obstacle avoidance
Temperature & humidity sensor grove - to measure temperature and humidity

bonus:

Servo with ir range detector to get point cloud


obstacle detection options and lidars tested -  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ddxguAzzzJE
